311
00:17:06,875 --> 00:17:11,083
That was just a fluke,
yeah, that's it.

312
00:17:11,166 --> 00:17:12,375
Koyomi, you're awesome!

313
00:17:12,458 --> 00:17:15,166
Koyomi, you looked really cool!

314
00:17:15,250 --> 00:17:17,541
