be right up Koyo's alley.

316
00:17:19,750 --> 00:17:22,166
But how could you
have known? Tell me!

317
00:17:22,250 --> 00:17:24,833
It's a little different
from Earth ping-pong,

318
00:17:24,916 --> 00:17:29,250
but we have a game on
Seiren called Pan Pon Pin.

319
00:17:29,333 --> 00:17:31,958
