by skill alone,

327
00:18:05,291 --> 00:18:08,875
but desperate times
call for desperate measures.

328
00:18:08,958 --> 00:18:11,750
Project S.

329
00:18:11,833 --> 00:18:14,041
I love you.

330
00:18:17,291 --> 00:18:19,750
Who's your daddy?

331
00:18:20,500 --> 00:18:22,958
Fukuyama!
You're just a cheating coward!

332
00:18:23,041 --> 00:18:25,666
I-I'm sorry. I can't...

333
