344
00:18:52,833 --> 00:18:57,125
Miharu, why are
you telling him that?

345
00:18:57,208 --> 00:19:01,041
I'm sorry. I forgot
about the polka dots, huh?

346
00:19:05,041 --> 00:19:07,250
Please, make it stop.

347
00:19:07,333 --> 00:19:08,791
Get a hold of yourself, Koyomi!

348
00:19:08,875 --> 00:19:11,083
You can't give up now!
If you lose this match,

349
00:19:11,166 --> 00:19:13,625
that cheating pervert's gonna
serve you up like a fruit salad!

350
00:19:13,708 --> 00:19:15,458
