the fat lady sings.

354
00:19:25,875 --> 00:19:26,458
Just pretend that ping-pong
ball is Fukuyama and hit it!

355
00:19:26,541 --> 00:19:30,833
Fukuyama's the ball?

356
00:19:30,916 --> 00:19:34,666
