Nineteen to nine!

368
00:20:27,166 --> 00:20:29,000
Yeah! You did it!
You won the match, Koyomi!

369
00:20:29,083 --> 00:20:32,125
Koyomi, you were amazing!

370
00:20:32,208 --> 00:20:34,166
